testSteps.description: Given James is logged into the application

children.description: James enters a valid user name
James enters 'enter your username in code before run test' into the user name input
James enters 'enter your password' into the password input
James clicks on the login submit button
James ensures that the table is available does become present

testSteps.description: And James is on the Add Sync page
When James enter a new Sync
Then James should see the synchronisation task

userStory.narrative:
In order to have BDD scenarios synchronised
As a user of the application
I would like to generate my own synchronisation task
